node.text: "But if we learned anything from sports, is that no matter how far down we may be, we are never too far down to come back."
The Houston-based rapper brings his workwear touch to Nike SB, adding bandana patterns, rope-style fat laces, and more to the fat-tongued gem.

node.text: So...are we calling these the "Reverse Royal"? This upcoming Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG "Dark Marina Blue" is set to release in early 2022; tap the link in our bio to see a closer look.

node.text: Reebok is set to drop the Kamikaze II decorated in those classic Spurs colors - a nod to the 1996 All-Star Game. Quite similar to the @packer "Remember The Alamo" collaboration from 2013! Hit the link in our bio for a closer look.

node.text: A great in-hand look at the upcoming Nike SB Dunk Low from September's Unbleached Pack has surfaces via @nikesbornothing. While the Dunk Lows already come dyed (hence the dye stains on the midsole), the accompanying Blazer and Dunk High were meant to be dyed at your own will. Fun bit of DIY with this latest Orange Label drop. Hit the link in our bio to see full official images; these are hitting skateshops this month.

node.text: #SNReleaseAlert : The adidas Yeezy Quantum "Onyx" is confirmed to release on September 10th, 2021; full family sizes are expected. Hit the link in our bio for more details.

node.text: Another colorway of the Nike ISPA Flow 2020 SE has emerged. This silhouette will release in mid-September, although the release date for this grey pair is still TBD. What are your first impressions on this model? Tap the link in our bio for a closer look.
